snippet.title: Hogwarts Legacy Haunted Hogsmeade Shop Quest Trailer | State of Play September 2022
snippet.description:
WB's Hogwarts Legacy gets a brand-new trailer showcasing the Harry Potter universe. Mannequins and darkness are unleashed, showcasing what could be the villain in this wizarding world game. Hogwart Legacy releases on February 10, 2023.

#hogwartslegacy #playstation #gaming #harrypotter
